OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Fsome showery rain in the evening. Then
OL,7,Fclear spells with a few showers moving
OL,8,Fthrough on the strong westerly or
OL,9,Fsouthwesterly breeze. It will be a
OL,10,Frather cold night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA bright day with sunny
OL,13,Fspells and a few passing showers.
OL,14,FFeeling rather cold with a fresh or
OL,15,Fstrong westerly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
