OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,6,Fand bright start Wednesday, but
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain later and
OL,8,Fstrengthening southerly winds. Rain
OL,9,Fbands moving east followed by drier
OL,10,Fand brighter spells for the rest of
OL,11,Fthe week.
